IebnPeTAumEttoG2QM-YqPmGD7ebGrQ0cpvHIpu2aSPtW16ewhTFObH1bX-6scDWEsjUvwKbjMPJ-N6gnCGMvJu6UafFcpeqe8h21puTDM0Gym0ghdIQM3V_cp2hmMjHmQHWKftNXUy5Rh3JONTc3SiUN2eKvyBp9k2qQtptnqNTOw4e5X91-wzOJZbfzge21bZyJTA4crDjm3PFTbXzRy5W3vJkNXTISp9QfX73_IsM/v38dMELz8XtTWOK_7IrELofX-S3OSthE/18"&gt;政治后果也可能会更加混乱&lt;/a&gt;。从革命卫队的分裂到库尔德叛乱，再到叙利亚式的真空，一切都明显混乱。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;迪拜的金融区：&lt;/strong&gt; ICD 布鲁克菲尔德广场的大堂为斋月而装饰，但塔楼却出奇的安静——没有银行家吸烟，也没有劳斯莱斯排队等候晚餐。冲突发生一周后，该&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/51NIKJD-9lX47YUi6TLjo8vbBI0AX8s0LiqqzKo6fyv360kwvH4lK3mN6dPtj7zC4_ZemaVI-VLVDqMvXb_n3d2WKwDBGlLOnFM3TCntMl7L4aPcxDRgWGxd-271k71cxXjzAvE3SKNLhNMONWP0Oz6Ntn9x0TeZ6n5KcJzq3myfV3pjrcK-dzPGKYnZHwPjyy4bHR4T3bdxBz0XB8VdHxvG1UpuwKtdqGDX-UvawKSGlOfD3zorg4T3MDhejUdbperQqng5DQcgGHWtSwwKTC6BbYmbJypYzjo_LgK0yxIVxaf7E7sGJDwgfY2pG7Si_3BXpTmvjPZBcLCHcVFWSUClQNUBTrZa3dN9GS7EBs2Nzn1CMQ_ISq0jlsw/7IlvVI2XThksvIknyc7I-acSBmiuZlha/18"&gt;地区“一反常态地空无一人”。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;华尔街：&lt;/strong&gt;市场出奇地平静，但约翰·奥瑟斯认为，投资者可能&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/55k1F8xTMAnR8owwmvwpXSHgE-On2djKPgerN1XLJO5se3Dbzu35VbrGZWA2ZeBbSyEImA1IUWgI9e7sPLP5iHUBJ7PO9sI1bdI6eyY-P_PejfcB2WCIjIMmMaiJaZwuQ6Bmkbc2zdGW_8FNoVxIDwcl9fWnTFaT249T_P5r-shqQ8WJgu-63wCnVyrt7PJhUMHMS65Z767JCUKX9C6DuME6aFX4TVULqrohCPgAmXRo8M1ccq8xdcBh8bQOMV1fQGbe8hYU1YLsWfir3KH2PUTH1Zb6EZjOx1rhDsAsNcqdv40DZg6iie0kNFGQSYheIhVOLZqpnPJr4paX_tRKxil0hdvoIJnK7zaVbCEyJl_Fd7hagMBPg5jQlnQ/uzHz6zZ0C6m94expPDi3gFY6bK0lqgoD/18"&gt;过于依赖历史令人安心的模式&lt;/a&gt;，即地缘政治冲击很快就会消退——如果这场战争演变成 1973 年那样的情况，这一教训就失效了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;1973 年：&lt;/strong&gt;阿拉伯石油禁运表明，能源供应的冲击如何&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/6qgoMXbjfkidCEk2r6ynf9sOI2j_kySNKNt98gCB4HEN-8I5IC6dGLas-21eJpwEIHNVpZYYnYWcarGy3N1uHbTaJcMpz6590YQjLJE2fHwv2J9OweIhk6SeV54i5LaDi9nD9LYBgPq6sUYvUvzlXRjHZL8lfB16q2y6_YID9w8lLXlX77PgZJ8rbPISmrC1k8fDFO9ab0xMrzpDMYfKRY36BspDVhsKvwuojo4BftkEkKVJptDI5oeXGttWw6rmVp6tN5EsT0Xckfdm4sODD8ohpXkD_CWT3pNyiYj_G4CLle6i4TFKVdoj65UneR-YUip6riovjpUfGARbo82MR1rYeQpPkXsaFBu5cYFXmbZ552bU5WEZe9blgDE/71mWaAoh5xUM0ox5wwVKr0KoUdRMXbat/18"&gt;演变成一场“全面危机”。&lt;/a&gt;中东战争很快波及全球经济，导致联盟关系紧张，并重塑了远离战场的日常生活。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;“Tehrangeles”：&lt;/strong&gt;在伊朗领导人去世的消息传出后，数千人在洛杉矶伊朗侨民的主干道上跳舞。其中一位说，她的父母“等待这一刻已经47年了”。但在欢腾的背后， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7bpk1LzhPEyUbCu6Kavujf3jgEROl_45htux89bdSV5pzh53dFrlSA6aBAgF075ZYbNY-bdwiGPgH4Q1InQ5iBtL0nmk3M2hIsEgndDwoXZUMQXF9rMjMs4ikcGX2wUrEbo-Eqw8P1Ox6eb6W2cIbdTPZ6UZpo0YE65mmRHs82L_iDr-cGoYUIH236TC96TIsZ-ko1vggCMn4x-dVUWj8ijMrFpzReGdU5IlY23laVDLcWilrzcluImcEsTxc_IZ5VyZVCEl-tDsdITS3Pw7uh8yUsHLLrj6GCyURiZxkJ9dfIproA8OMRGsoQXnWwAkmDXvnpMIWvxll3w4WVAkm2qzvVY43PVvOCTwIoaocFRJcTzGuLqLCEVqbmU/r5zIY595gg4f35nxHZD-0ufBG3BBwtwk/18"&gt;侨民内心却充满矛盾&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7L7fO0FwKVUGe8S56exidLOWzfRVOv1caoFbqgK0HwDSnI1oa-LPqunxIZ-X4diLkLS6To3DLjB6RN4aEj4xbh6rcsVKaMjWnCWv8sssnPiSFW1G9GCZ13kOHd6znLBPujt-Hti_CTRfpIDwtPCO61jjTfLpnKauWdtzb0QXXUlUSZ7443Zi9MKdFMpBGz0QhXwkmNlIqyzrP8YLKNSUz9BS8eezMO7a8CKXSt6qlvTe0q7AAGSlqSxOcKnZRr5kekJvMIggxS3lkFqbxURgbW_CirzCAQdu09DXKnNM3xwhcMGzfi_GijDowGUjDTSCrlSPjXVuXemSbMQjQOxA4LZBs4aMNB4Y5gS-1TMDo14_5hj1qpLYQlbcwe8/49AgK50XPAAnhptsfuor0I60FenRCg8m/18" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iymVjQ9glAos/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display: